sentences.english: Like every paradigm throughout history, at some point or another, things change.
sentences.chinese: 正如历史上所有的范例一样，世事常变，无物永驻。

sentences.english: Example topic page is also available.
sentences.chinese: 技能首页也可以看作范例分类总页。

sentences.english: It is the longest standing example of interagency cooperation in the UN system.
sentences.chinese: 它是联合国系统最悠久的机构间合作范例。

sentences.english: African delegates said they hope to learn from Vietnam's agricultural example.
sentences.chinese: 非洲与会代表说，他们希望向越南的农业范例学习。

sentences.english: A perfect example of how you can say a lot by saying very little.
sentences.chinese: 一个“微言大义”式的完美范例。

sentences.english: Taobao makes for a nice example of the symbiotic relationship between consumption and innovation.
sentences.chinese: 淘宝网成就了一个创新与消费之间典型关系的范例。

sentences.english: The operation was a marvel of medical skill.
sentences.chinese: 这个手术是医术的一个非凡范例。

sentences.english: This effective inheritance education of the birth consciousness in Zhan Li is a quite typical and successful instance.
sentences.chinese: 占里生育自觉的有效传承就是一个极为典型的范例。

sentences.english: There was no end of parallel cases and these made precedents to guide me.
sentences.chinese: 这些平行发展没有止境的案例成为指导我的范例。

sentences.english: Mr Hu hopes Xinhe will be an example to the world.
sentences.chinese: 胡占平希望新河村能成为世界上一个范例。

sentences.english: This is a good example of his lyric poetry.
sentences.chinese: 这首诗是他抒情诗的范例。

sentences.english: Up to now, China has been the poster child for market-oriented economic reform success.
sentences.chinese: 迄今为止，中国一直是推行市场经济改革的成功范例。

sentences.english: They have to meet all types of people.
sentences.chinese: 他们得战各种范例的人挨交讲。

sentences.english: Retinal directional selectivity is a classic example of neurocomputation.
sentences.chinese: 视网膜方向选择性是神经计算的一个典型范例。

sentences.english: This example displays a semi-colon delimited list of current symbol paths.
sentences.chinese: 此范例将两个路径加入至符号目录清单。

sentences.english: Multi-paradigm parallelism is the characteristic of large-scale parallel application systems.
sentences.chinese: 多范例并行是大规模并行应用系统的本质特征。

definition: to draw on (others' experience)/to learn from (how others do things)/lesson to be learned (by observing others)
practice/to put into practice/to live up to (a promise)/to carry out (a project)
to demonstrate/to show how to do sth/demonstration/a model example
